  "text": "Generally, the operating frequency provided by EDA tools tends to be conservative to ensure the correct functionality under a wide range of operating environments and workloads. In a practical situation, this may result in a large gap between the predicted frequency and the actual frequency under which the correct operation is maintained [CITATION_1] .",
